    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit features a crisp M-DCT dual-clutch gearbox and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The vehicle is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension remain dialed in. Recent service includes a comprehensive inspection of the VANOS system and fresh performance-grade fluids. While the paint shows minor patina from spirited use, the structural integrity and powertrain performance are uncompromising. A true enthusiast's driver that balances track-ready kinematics with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
